ered form of Irish   Crilly  ."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When John de Cailly was born in 1165, in Cranwich, Norfolk, England, his father, John De Cailly Lord of Massingham, was 16 and his mother, Beatrice de Butery, was 16. He married Margaret about 1184, in Poynings, Sussex, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. He died in 1202, in Oxborough, Norfolk, England, at the age of 37."},"et":{"1165–1202":"1165–1202","–Female":"Surnud","1164–Female":"1164–Surnud","1192–1262":"1192–1262","1202–Male":"1202–Surnud","1150–1202":"1150–1202","1150–Female":"1150–Surnud","about 1184":"umbes 1184","1202":"1202","1165":"1165","BEF 1202":"enne 1202","1164":"1164","1262":"1262","1150":"1150","Abt 1192":"1192","1192":"1192","Cranwich, Norfolk, England":"Cranwich, Norfolk, England","Poynings, Sussex, England":"Poynings, Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England"},"fi":{"1165–1202":"1165–1202","–Female":"Kuollut","1164–Female":"1164–Kuollut","1192–1262":"1192–1262","1202–Male":"1202–Kuollut","1150–1202":"1150–1202","1150–Female":"1150–Kuollut","about 1184":"noin 1184","1202":"1202","1165":"1165","BEF 1202":"ennen vuotta 1202","1164":"1164","1262":"1262","1150":"1150","Abt 1192":"1192","1192":"1192","Cranwich, Norfolk, England":"Cranwich, Norfolk, England","Poynings, Sussex, England":"Poynings, Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England"},"fr":{"1165–1202":"1165–1202","–Female":"Décédée","1164–Female":"1164–Décédée","1192–1262":"1192–1262","1202–Male":"1202–Décédé","1150–1202":"1150–1202","1150–Female":"1150–Décédée","about 1184":"environ 1184","1202":"1202","1165":"1165","BEF 1202":"avant 1202","1164":"1164","1262":"1262","1150":"1150","Abt 1192":